        "description": "Relative hemolysis index (RH) and normalised index of hemolysis (NIH) compared between CFD predictions and bench measurements at all five operating points. Maximum relative error is 14.3% (at 6 L/min, 3500 rpm); all points within the ±20% acceptance band. Validation metric computed per ASME V&V 20-2009 framework."
