        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Material properties and geometric inputs traceable to calibrated measurements",
        "description": "Blood analogue viscosity measured with a cone-and-plate rheometer (±2%); density measured gravimetrically (±0.1%). Pump geometry digitised from manufacturer drawings with CMM verification (±10 µm). All input values and their uncertainties documented in the model input specification MIS-GCBP-2022-01."
      },
      "rationale": "All material and geometric inputs are traceable to calibrated measurements with documented uncertainty. Gradation 2 requirement satisfied."
